gn=\"center\">Y</p>\r    <td class=\"date\">3&nbsp;Tu\r    <td rowspan=\"2\">Modeling</td>\r    <td>Introduction to Modeling </td>\r      <td rowspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Chapter 6 </td>\r      <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">&nbsp;</td>\r</tr>\r\r  <tr>\r    <td class=\"date\">5&nbsp;Th\r    <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Modeling and Notations</td>\r    <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" class=\"due\">&nbsp;</td>\r  </tr>\r\r  <tr>\r    <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"week\"> 6    <!-- - - - - - - -7- - - - - - - -->\r    <td class=\"date\">10&nbsp;Tu\r    <td>Visualization</td>\r    <td>Visualizing Software Architectures </td>\r    <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Chapter 7 </td>\r      <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">&nbsp;</td>\r  </tr>\r\r\r  <tr>\r    <td class=\"date\">12&nbsp;Th\r    <td>Homework #1 preview session</td>\r    <td>Student-developed models</td>\r    <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">&nbsp;</td>\r    <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" class=\"due\">&nbsp;</td>\r  </tr>\r\r  <tr>\r    <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"week\"> 7    <!-- - - - - - - -8- - - - - - - -->\r    <td height=\"46\" class=\"date\">17&nbsp;Tu</td>\r    <td>Analysis</td>\r      <td>Analysis of Software Architectures </td>\r    <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Chapter 8 (selections) </td>\r      <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Homework #1 due</td>\r      <!--\r      <td><a\rhref=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~taylor/ICS221/slides/ICS221CSCWDourish.ppt\">Computer-supported cooperative work</a>\r      <td class=\"ok\">Dourish\r      <td><a\rhref=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~redmiles/ics221-FQ03/papers/AO00.pdf\">[AO00]</a>\r      <br><a\rhref=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~redmiles/ics221-FQ03/papers/Gru94.pdf\">[Gru94]</a>\r      -->\r  </tr>\r\r  <tr>\r    <td height=\"46\" class=\"date\">19&nbsp;Th\r    <td rowspan=\"2\">Implementation    </td>\r    <td>Implementing Architectures</td>\r\t<td rowspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Chapter 9 </td>\r\t<td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" class=\"due\">&nbsp;</td>\r  </tr>\r\r  <tr>\r    <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"week\"> 8    <!-- - - - - - - -9- - - - - - - -->\r    <td class=\"date\">24&nbsp;Tu\r    <td><a href=\"MyxTutorial.pdf\">Implementation Techniques \r    </a>\r    (Asuncion)<td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">&nbsp;</td>\r  </tr>\r\r\r  <tr>\r    <td class=\"date\"> 26 &nbsp;Th\r    <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Architectures in the Real-World </td>\r    <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Applied Architectures: P2P systems</td>\r    <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Chapter 11 </td>\r    <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" class=\"due\"><p><a href=\"http://tps.ics.uci.edu/svn/projects/archstudio4/documents/INF123_LL_EnvSetup.pdf\">More\r            help with the existing lunar lander example</a></p>\r        <p><a href=\"MyxDemo.pdf\">Today's slides</a></p></td>\r  </tr>\r\r  <tr>\r    <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"week\"> 9    <!-- - - - - - - 10- - - - - - -->\r    <td width=\"7%\" rowspan=\"5\" align=\"center\" class=\"date\">     <p>M</p>\r      <p>A</p>\r      <p>R</p>\r      <p>C</p>\r      <p>H    </p>\r    <td class=\"date\">3&nbsp;Tu</td>\r\r      <td><em>No class. </em></td>\r    <td>&nbsp;</td>\r      <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">&nbsp;</td>\r\t  <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">&nbsp;</td>\r  </tr>\r\r\r  <tr>\r    <td class=\"date\">5&nbsp;Th</td>\r      <td>Architectures in the Real-World </td>\r      <td>Applied Architectures </td>\r      <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Chapter 11 </td>\r      <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" class=\"due\">&nbsp;</td>\r  </tr>\r\r\r  <tr>\r    <td rowspan=\"2\" class=\"week\">10      \r    <td class=\"date\">10&nbsp;Tu</td>\r      <td rowspan=\"2\">Domain-Specific Software Engineering </td>\r      <td>Introduction to DSSE </td>\r      <td rowspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\">Chapter 15 </td>\r      <td bgcolor=\"#FFFFFF\" class=\"due\">&nbsp;</td>\r  </tr>\r\r\r  <tr>\r    <td class=\"date\">12 Th </td>\r    <td>DSSE and Product Lines </td>\r    <td>Homework #2 due</td>\r  </tr>\r  <tr><td class=\"week\" rowspan=\"1\">Exam <!-- - - - - - -Exam - - - - - -->\r    <td class=\"date\">17 Tu </td>\r      <td>&nbsp;</td>\r      <td>Exam\r          from 4:00 -- 6:00</td>\r      <td><span class=\"style1\"></span></td>\r      <td>&nbsp;</td>\r  </tr>\r</table>\r\r<hr width=\"100%\">\r\r<h3><font face=\"Verdana\"><a name=\"grading\"></a>Grading and\rEvaluations</font></h3>\r\r<p><b>Grading.</b><br>\rThere are 3 elements to your grade: a final exam, homework,  and class\r  attendance and participation.\r<p><strong>Summary of Assessment: </strong> </p>\r<table summary=\"Grading\">\r  <tr>\r    <td>Homework</td>\r    <td>70%<br>\r  </tr>\r  <tr>\r    <td>Final exam </td>\r    <td>20%<br>\r  </tr>\r  <tr>\r    <td>Class attendance and participation</td>\r    <td>10%</td>\r  </tr>\r  <!--\r  <tr>\r  \t<td>Final exam</td>\r  \t<td>20%</td>\r  </tr>\r-->\r</table>\r<p> No grades of incomplete (I) will be given for this course.&nbsp;</p>\r<hr width=\"100%\">\r\r\r<h3><font face=\"Verdana\"><a\rname=\"policies\"></a>Policies</font></h3>\r\r<p><b>Course Evalutions. </b>The online evaluation window for winter quarter\r  will run from TBA through TBA.  </p>\r<p><b>Cheating. </b>The <a\rhref=\"http://www.senate.uci.edu/senateweb/printed.asp?active_page_id=754\">UCI\r  academic honesty policy</a> applies. Consequences of\r  cheating in this class:\r  a letter in your UCI file, and the course grade is lowered,\r  most likely to\r  F. Material that is copied from books or Web pages needs to\r  be quoted and\r  the source <em>must</em> be given.  If you plagarize, you run the severe risk\r  of failing the class, in a most disgraceful manner. </p>\r<p><b>Disabilities. </b> If you need an accommodation\rbecause of a disability, please contact\rthe instructor and the <a\rhref=\"http://www.disability.uci.edu/\">Disability Services\rCenter</a> as soon as possible.\r\r<hr width=\"100%\">\r\r<font face=\"Verdana\"><font size=\"-1\"><br>\r<i><font\rsize=\"-1\">(C) University of California, 2009.\r</font></i></font>\r</font>\r</body></html>\r\r\r<!--\r<td><a\rhref=\"other/ics221.formalSpecification.2004.ppt\">Formal\rspecification methods</a></td>\r      <td class=\"ok\">Alspaugh\r      <td><a\rhref=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/%7Etaylor/ICS221/papers/e1089.pdf\">[vLW98]</a>\r\r      <br><a\rhref=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/%7Etaylor/ICS221/papers/HLK95.pdf\">[HLK95]</a>\r\r\r      <td class=\"ok\">Scenario analysis\r      <td><span class=\"ok\">Alspaugh</span>\r      <td><a\rhref=\"http://springerlink.metapress.com/link.asp?id=v90uxu73cw29drka\">[AP98]</a>\r      <br><a\rhref=\"http://doi.acm.org/10.1145/225434.225462\">[Pot95]</a>\r\r\r\r-->\r", "encoding": "ascii"}